- [ ] Data shown matches the actual run state; timing breakdown aligns with per-step data; diffs accurately reflect changes.
- [ ] UI adheres to the design system: dark UI, typography, spacing, colors, and responsive behavior.
- [ ] Accessibility: keyboard navigable, ARIA attributes present, color contrast compliant.

