- Cronjob Editor: Provide quick navigation to edit the associated cronjob; reflect current cronjob config if required.
- Agent Trace & Debugger: Deep-dive tool; link to detailed agent conversation graph and scoped memory for this run.
- Audit Trail & Reversibility: Display immutable logs and reversible actions with validators in the Reversibility panel.
- Conflict Resolution Engine: Show explainable decisions and related run decisions where conflicts occurred.
- Cronjobs Engine: Show next run time and past run outcomes; provide access to run history.
- Scoped Memory Store: Show memory scope and encrypted data indicators if applicable.

Notes for AI Development Tool
